/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image presents a panoramic view of a street in Beijing, China. The perspective is from a high angle, providing a bird's eye view of the scene. The street is lined with lush green trees, their leaves forming a canopy overhead. Parked cars are neatly lined up along the side of the road, adding a touch of urban life to the otherwise serene setting. Buildings of various sizes and designs flank the street, their facades reflecting the architectural diversity of the city. The sky above is a clear blue, with a few clouds scattered across it, adding depth to the expansive view. The colors in the image are predominantly green from the trees, blue from the sky, and gray from the buildings, creating a harmonious palette that is pleasing to the eye.
